If you wanted to play a diagonal move at 1, it's because you memorized the pattern incorrectly.

Please check <\b Basic Diagram 40\b0 > once again.

It is a good sacrifice strategy for black to play dansu at 2 and attach with 4.

Up to 6, black seals white in perfectly in seonsu and then extends at 8 and has very impressive influence.
