;B[mn]LB[mr:1][lp:2][lq:3][mp:4][mn:5]C[Diagram 3 (Spiral Ladder)


This is also an addional explanation.

When black plays dansu with 1, if white captures with 2, white is in trouble.

Black can drive white out with 3 and 5, creating a ladder. This type of ladder is called a spiral ladder.

Be sure to watch out for it!
])
